Class AdvanceData

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.api.core.AdvanceData

  • public final class AdvanceData
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience utils to extract or create values from various default ADVANCE XElement objects.
    Author:
    akarnokd, 2011.11.04.
